{
  "stem": "26609.17",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I came over, first I had to start working there, because I was still there, until they got together a big-- 8,000 people, a transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to be the one who went with them, because there was no one else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was only an American captain of the-- it wasn't a normal train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Again, they put together some wooden carriages for a train with a machine, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Somewhere, they constructed a train for 8,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was only an American officer, captain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had to have someone going to all those different countries to get in contact with the officials.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was only one for 8,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was the paper I have here when I arrived in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on the way, I had-- people were ill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First of all, they gave me food that I had to-- in those Red Cross packages, cartons of some food, [INAUDIBLE] what was there, I don't even remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the one carriage of that train, we kept all the food under the key.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had the key.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Otherwise, the people would take it out, everything, under the key.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And once daily, I had to give rations to 8,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I couldn't find myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had to have someone, a helper, there, two helpers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I was the only one, no one else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They didn't have enough-- among the people were somewhere, someone else's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they had to look after the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "On the way, I had a few corpses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "People died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had just a limited supply of some-- some injections and some drugs, some tablets, something like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
